                    h1 Pedagogical Council

                .decptext.text-start.mb-5.pb-5
                    p.lead The Pedagogical Council is organized in Course Committees and in Assemblies, instances functionally articulated within the scope of the IPB Statutes. The Assembly of the Pedagogical Council is made up of the President of the Pedagogical Council, the Course Directors and one student from each course.


